          <h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2019/06/sunday-assorted-links-220.html">Sunday assorted links</a></h2>
    
      <div class="byline">
        by&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="author"><a href="/about">Tyler Cowen</a></span>
        <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2019-06-30 14:18:27">June 30, 2019 at 2:18 pm </time>
                                          </div><!-- /.byline -->
  </header><!-- /.entry-header -->
  <div class="entry-content">
    <div class="pf-content"><p>1. <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/books/2019/jun/27/melvil-deweys-name-stripped-from-top-librarian-award" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">The American Library Association cancels Melvil Dewey, inventor of the Dewey Decimal system</a>.</p>
<p>2. <a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/business-48769620" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Investing in hit songs</a>.</p>
<p>3. <a href="https://www.adn.com/politics/alaska-legislature/2019/06/28/gov-mike-dunleavy-vetoes-444-million-from-alaska-state-operating-budget/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Fiscal choices facing Alaska</a>.</p>
<p>4. <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/AskReddit/comments/b7ssbh/what_are_some_recent_scientific/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Underrated recent scientific developments</a>? (speculative)</p>
<p>5. <a href="https://www.theamericanconservative.com/articles/americas-monopoly-crisis-hits-the-military/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Industrial capacity as a public good</a>?</p>
<p>6. <a href="https://twitter.com/wwwojtekk/status/1145179535039594496" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">The wealth of the top one percent</a>?</p>
</div>
