            <article class="post-76229 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized" id="post-76229">
  <header class="entry-header">

          <h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2019/06/thursday-assorted-links-213.html">Friday assorted links</a></h2>
    
      <div class="byline">
        by&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="author"><a href="/about">Tyler Cowen</a></span>
        <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2019-06-28 12:27:01">June 28, 2019 at 12:27 pm </time>
                                          </div><!-- /.byline -->
  </header><!-- /.entry-header -->
  <div class="entry-content">
    <div class="pf-content"><p>1. &#8220;<a href="https://www.pnas.org/content/early/2019/06/18/1814688116" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Our results suggest that Americans overestimate the intergenerational persistence in income ranks. They overestimate economic prospects for children from rich families and underestimate economic prospects for those from poor families.</a>&#8221;</p>
<p>2. <a href="https://medium.com/swlh/how-much-money-can-you-actually-make-writing-articles-on-medium-e9855c255485" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">The economics of writing on Medium</a>.</p>
<p>3. How are consumers responding to nudges? <a href="https://behavioralscientist.org/consumers-are-becoming-wise-to-your-nudge/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Are they counteracting them</a>?</p>
<p>4. <a href="https://www.theatlantic.com/ideas/archive/2019/06/neurodiversity-truth-telling/592465/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Neurodiversity and dissent</a>.</p>
<p>5. <a href="https://medium.com/@the_i_i/as-we-may-adult-ea67eef10ccc" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">The moral luck of adulthood</a>.</p>
<p>6. <a href="https://www.reuters.com/article/us-taiwan-china-campaign-insight/pro-china-groups-step-up-offensive-to-win-over-taiwan-idUSKCN1TR01H" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">The Taiwanese party that advocates actual unification with mainland China</a>.</p>
<p>7. <a href="https://www.nature.com/news/stem-cells-egg-engineers-1.13582" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Creating sperm and eggs</a> (!).</p>
</div>
  </div><!-- /.entry-content -->
