            <article class="post-76236 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized" id="post-76236">
  <header class="entry-header">

          <h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2019/06/friday-assorted-links-216.html">Thursday assorted links</a></h2>
    
      <div class="byline">
        by&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="author"><a href="/about">Tyler Cowen</a></span>
        <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2019-06-27 12:04:49">June 27, 2019 at 12:04 pm </time>
                                          </div><!-- /.byline -->
  </header><!-- /.entry-header -->
  <div class="entry-content">
    <div class="pf-content"><p>1. <a href="https://twitter.com/wesyang/status/1143838477076893696?s=12" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">&#8220;&#8230;at a cost of 600,000&#8221;!</a></p>
<p>2. <a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/education/democrats-abandon-charter-schools-as-reform-agenda-falls-from-favor/2019/06/25/3cf4817e-904e-11e9-aadb-74e6b2b46f6a_story.html?utm_term=.4601b9ca75e0" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Democrats are abandoning the idea of charter schools</a>.</p>
<p>3. <a href="https://www.nber.org/papers/w25998" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Productivity for non-employer firms</a>.</p>
<p>4. <a href="https://twitter.com/RTEOne/status/1143996266474541066?s=20" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Irish greyhound markets in everything</a>.</p>
<p>5. <a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2019-06-26/unbanked-consumers-may-not-need-facebook-s-libra-currency?srnd=opinion" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Adam Minter on Libra</a>.</p>
<p>6. <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/europes-struggling-political-parties-promise-a-return-to-the-1970s-11561561071" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Mega-statism is returning to Europe</a> (WSJ).</p>
</div>
  </div><!-- /.entry-content -->
